{"tid":1641430,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"Tiffany識玩","createTime":"2019-10-09T10:32:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-09T18:01:47.000Z","uid":193217,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"08ba2a316cc66882e641d118b4b73f17766d1398","tid":1641430,"uid":193217,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T10:32:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ar55Fr3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Far55Fr3.png&h=705d7536&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n大陸已經控制唔到佢地班小粉紅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a2409c7a6a9c66e363ca7f169002e33d3dc72dfb","tid":1641430,"uid":193217,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T10:33:27.000Z","msg":"在時尚界的雜誌封面或平面廣告上，妝容精緻的模特或明星以手遮住一隻眼睛的動作是很常見的。然而，知名珠寶名牌Tiffany最新推出的一張模特遮眼的廣告圖，卻意外碰觸到了中共小粉紅們的「玻璃心」，在中國的網絡社交媒體上被狂轟「辱華」，以至於被宣布迫停用這張廣告圖。台媒感嘆中共洗腦教育出來的「強國人」，原來心靈如此脆弱。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"459bf84f328f552470f61964faef984419903b39","tid":1641430,"uid":182519,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T10:34:04.000Z","msg":"國際文宣組全面進化，大型國際文宣活動&quot;What if they own it&quot;<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1639378\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1639378</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"670f332d62efa544a775164aeae221a3f3efc69e","tid":1641430,"uid":